r to do it by herself, so she called on the help of all the other members of the secret society. Together, they were able to reverse the spell and bring back everyone's original kindness. They didn't want to take control over the king's army, though. They just wanted to teach him a lesson. They went back to the evil king's palace and offered to teach him about kindness and generosity.

